# Project Charter - LED_POV

## SD_403_Sp24_06 LED Spinner

### Deliverables

Design an LED spinning display than can produce an image and video production. Along with the LED display, design the motor to power the project, as well as a stand to hold all apparatus'

### Key Elements

Must Haves:

- Display Images
- Electric Motor
- Motor Controller
- Main controller (MCU)
- Stand
- AC Powered (Wall Outlet)

Nice to Have:

- Windows compatible Display
- Interactive Element for Display
- Detachable from stand
- Quiet (Low Air-Resistance)

### Time Allocated

2 Semesters

### Budget

$300 USD
